Description
This Python script scrapes news articles related to the share price of Reliance Industries from Google News and performs sentiment analysis on the content of these articles.
The purpose of this code is to provide insights into the sentiment surrounding Reliance Industries' share price by analyzing recent news articles.
The script utilizes the GoogleNews library to fetch news articles, extracts the content from the articles' HTML pages using BeautifulSoup, and then analyzes the sentiment of the extracted content. 
Sentiment analysis is performed to determine whether the tone of the news articles is positive, negative, or neutral regarding Reliance Industries' share price.
This tool can be useful for investors, financial analysts, or anyone interested in tracking public sentiment regarding Reliance Industries' performance in the stock market.
